></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n<br />\n1.放飛黑氣球 <br />\n<br />\n2. 唱國歌 願榮光<br />\n<br />\n3. 揮萬國旗  chinazi旗當然唔少得<br />\n<br />\n4. 摺紙鳥 一齊飛<br />\n<br />\n5. 帶文宣（共慘黨罪證 最好有英文啦）周圍貼 <br />\n<br />\n6. 共產黨旗習近平遺照貼滿港島 整條黃泉路比佢<br />\n<br />\n7. 全世界搵布蒙眼一分鐘，聲援新疆集中營手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（可能死埋）<br />\n<br />\n8. 全民帶樣黃色野出席舉起，We are not yellow object!<br />\n<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">參與當日每人起碼做三樣</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>930 </strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n<br />\n全城大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBrainstorm仲左D咩搶第二日國際頭版<br />\n<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>101</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\nV煞<br />\n<br />\n（地點我覺得我地而家拋反個波比政府先，唔比港島就各區玩大佢）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>提議覺得ok or可以再討論幫我推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />P牌推唔郁 推到有文宣！你見個熱門仲係一個行動熱門都冇😭😭出post都冇quota！或者有冇人可以有系統D整合分工？ D行動都唔好一次出曬，每次唔同分佈黎近幾日會好有image！ </strong></span>"},{"pid":"49933646404aa88988e81e32b5501b160736e0e7","tid":1592492,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:14:54.000Z","msg":"13"},{"pid":"49dc83e1fbc6be4a9fc1e1db30b47f2b4b9ac1d2","tid":1592492,"uid":145194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:16:33.000Z","msg":"班撚樣冇良心嘅，實話能夠架"},{"pid":"7fe2b7627bc44f204fed331535e7362498a4d448","tid":1592492,"uid":166634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:17:17.000Z","